### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### NOTES - Cahier de laboratoire
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Configuration (Dev)
@host = http://localhost:8080
@auth = {{host}}/api/auth
@api = {{host}}/api/notes

### ─── Login ───
POST {{auth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken); %}

### ─── Créer une note ───
POST {{api}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Protocole PCR",
  "content": "1. Extraction ADN\n2. Amplification\n3. Électrophorèse\n4. Analyse des résultats",
  "color": "blue",
  "pinned": false,
  "tags": ["protocole", "pcr", "biologie-moleculaire"]
}

### ─── Créer une seconde note (épinglée) ───
POST {{api}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Rappels sécurité labo",
  "content": "- Port du EPI obligatoire\n- Hotte aspirante pour les solvants\n- Décontamination des surfaces",
  "color": "red",
  "pinned": true,
  "tags": ["sécurité", "important"]
}

### ─── Lister mes notes ───
GET {{api}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Détail d'une note (ID=1) ───
GET {{api}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Mettre à jour une note ───
PUT {{api}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Protocole PCR v2",
  "content": "1. Extraction ADN (kit Qiagen)\n2. Amplification (35 cycles)\n3. Électrophorèse (gel 1.5%)\n4. Analyse UV",
  "tags": ["protocole", "pcr", "biologie-moleculaire", "v2"]
}

### ─── Toggle pin ───
PATCH {{api}}/1/pin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Rechercher ───
GET {{api}}/search?q=protocole
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Supprimer une note ───
DELETE {{api}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
